flowchart TD
    Start([Worker Starts Job]) --> Exec[Execute Handler Logic]
    
    Exec --> Result{Execution Result?}
    
    Result -- Success --> Ack[XACK & XDEL Main Stream Message]
    Result -- NonRetryableError --> DLQ[Write to DLQ Stream & XACK]
    
    Result -- Transient Error --> CheckAttempt{Attempt < 5?}
    
    CheckAttempt -- No --> DLQ
    CheckAttempt -- Yes --> Calc[Calculate Backoff: base * 5^attempt-1]
    
    Calc --> ZAdd[ZADD jobs:service:delayed execute_at payload]
    ZAdd --> AckOriginal[XACK & XDEL Original Stream Message]
    
    subgraph Delayed Queue Loop
        ZAdd --> Wait[Wait in ZSET until execute_at timestamp]
        Wait --> LoopCheck[Worker checks ZRANGEBYSCORE 0 now]
        LoopCheck --> ReEnqueue[XADD jobs:service payload]
        ReEnqueue --> ZRem[ZREM jobs:service:delayed payload]
    end

    ReEnqueue --> Start
